{"tid":366911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聲援良心犯】上台講旺角騷亂 梁天琦：佢哋唔係鬼 係命運共同體","createTime":"2017-08-20T11:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T09:43:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73d6475e66f91110ef91b2adfa1886fe2583a559","tid":366911,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170820/large/1503225166_2a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170820%2Flarge%2F1503225166_2a36.jpg&h=b215b1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16名入獄年青政治犯的朋友陸續上台分享，其中本土民主前線梁天琦和黃台仰上台時獲得全場掌聲。梁天琦說，今日的集會未必有用是現實，但全靠多年前起，自己開始上街反高鐵反政改等，才造就今日的梁天琦，「正係參與無用嘅示威集會，今日先會上台、今日先會背負暴動罪。看似無用嘅集會，會繼續影響更多人」。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦指，下一代會指向今代人，問為何無為2047年付出，但已有年輕人因旺角年初一等事件入獄，「佢哋唔係鬼，係香港命運共同體，只要有人受苦，就係我受苦，所以我要行出嚟」。他說，當下一代回望和指向他時，也能抬頭挺胸說：「我有付出過」。"},{"pid":"257d099d03553bcba3de7d4ba9c3b90515900fd5","tid":366911,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"最弊付出到二零四七都係咩都冇，好似買樓咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f8967f7c10e5f3fdaacc84b39db0b4adc205e5","tid":366911,"uid":59238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f3dac62761c20b79795dc02a4c997410310a96","tid":366911,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好死"}]}